values: I'm soo fucking excited!!!!!!!! I finally got Kevin's CD. I had been waiting for like 2 months for him to give me his cd. He also gave me a flyer for his next performance for tonight. I can't go. I have to be 21 or older to get into the club. BUMMER!!! I'm going to find out where I can get a fake ID. JUST KIDDING!!!!!! Anyway, I listened to his cd. Really good stuff!!!!! I wish I was 21 with a car and was able to go and check him out in L.A. He is a hottie!
I buried George this morning. It was hard to do.
George died. I loved my turtle.
I just remembered.... IT'S PAYDAY TODAY!!! Money for my car.
I can't count on my parents for anything.

I'm so happy!!! I just bought a turtle!!! I love turtles. I haven't named it yet. I'm planning to buy like 3 more. I want to name them after the Beatles. I also bought Aladdin on VHS for $4 and a humongo sea shell for $1.
Well, school is almost over. My last day of work is June 9th. Yey! Then I'll have time to hang out with my friends.

I just spoke to Ruby on the phone. It made us realize that it had been a while since the last time that I've hung out with my friends. I miss hanging out. No..really! I MISS HANGING OUT WITH MY FRIENDS!!!!!!!!!!!!

<FONT color=#6633ff>So yeah, now I'm officially known as the "porn chick." Well, this started like 2 weeks ago. It was my friend's birthday. I decided that it would be fun if I bought my friend a porn video. Well, yeah it was my first time buying a porn video, so yeah....I felt kinda weird. I went to go pay for it. Some guy I like works there so yeah I was really hoping that he wouldn't see me. Anyway, well it was taking forever because I get a discount for working at the mall. She didn't have functions to do that, so she had to get her supervisor. We waited a while. The video was just sitting on the counter. I wished that at least she would put it in the bag or something, but no. I was just there, still hoping the she would put it away so that no embarassing thing would happen. Then out of nowhere, Sean (the guy that I have a crush on) was like "Hey!" I said hi. OMG! He looked at it. I told him that it wasn't what he thinks it is. He was just like "I'm sure it's not" OMG I WANTED TO DIE RIGHT THEN AND THERE. I saw him later on that day and he asked me what was up with the video. I told him why I was getting it. He understood. I was still embarrassed though. So yeah, I bummped into that same cashier yesterday. She called me the "porn chick." We just laughed about it though. </FONT>

<FONT color=#3366ff>Wow, it's been a while hasn't it? Omg! I have the biggest crush on this one guy! I just talked to him on the phone. I'm currenlty talking to my old friend Josh. He's a cool guy. A really cool guy. I'd  go out with him if I could.</FONT>

My favorite pink purse was stolen! Geez, that was my favorite purse with my favorte 2 cds in them! I can't believe that my Green Day "American Idiot" and Hoobastank "The Reason" cds are completely gone. Oh yeah, and I had money in there too! Crap!

New semester, new schedule. I've had so much free time for myself. Yey! I'm okay with that. Haha, speaking of free time, I've actually been watching The Power Rangers....the original series. I still can't believe that they still show those episodes! Brings back memories. It actually comes out on Toon Disney @5pm. I hope, I hope, I hope that I will be able to get my turtle this weekend! I REALLY want one! I've been talking to Peter more often now. He's so bloody cool!

I went to church with Gaby today. It was so funny. The pastor said something like "You know you are getting old when your dream car is a mini van." LOL! Anyway, I consider myself a tolerant, accepting and a giving person, but some of the things that were said at church today upset me. Basically, the guy said that being a "worldly" person is bad and learning about other things in the world is bad because "you are forgetting the lord." I just think that people should be tolerant of others and their surroundings, good or bad. I just don't think that someone should shut other people out just because of what they like or what they decide to do. Then again, I'm not of that religion. I just disaggree with what was said.

Anyway, later on I went to Costco. Geez, there were sooo many people there! I had fun taste testing the flavored water =). I have to memorize Hamlet's "To be or not to be" speech by Tuesday! I really need to get going on it because the speech is kinda long. It's actuallly my final for english. I have to present it in front of 2 teachers, 1 administrator and my class.

Gee whiz, have I have been studious today. I just finished studying for my Art History test tomorrow. I also finished my Government homework (I had a lot of it.) I also finished my Chemistry homework. I had a good day! I helped Nancy finish her lamp shade during Stain Glass. I'm also almost finished with my jewelry box. I should be done with it in a day or two.

I went to the DMV today. I took the written part of my test for the 1st time. I passed! Damn, I'm good! Haha, lol no I'm not. Woo-hoo!!! I had a blast during break. I was so happy to see everyone at school. Then I saw my bestfriend Mamie after school. I was so happy because I didn't get to see her at all during break. I took a nap when I came home. I bearly made it upstair to my room. I was so tired.
I had the best surprize birthday party!!!!! I totally did not have a clue about it. My friends are so bloody awesome!!!!!

Oh my G-word!!! I haven't like updated this thing in a while! Anyway, yeah I've obviously haven't had time to write in this thing. Hmm yeah. My birthday is in like 14 days. I've already been promised a turtle =) I hope I get it cause yeah I've been wanting one for a while. I love turtles! I used to have one a long time ago. Anyway, I've just been really busy with visiting colleges and stuff. Man, I had this one really crazy dream last night. In my dream, My art history teacher (Mrs. Powell) thought I was cheating on the test that we were taking. I wasn't cheating though. Anyway, she took my test. I got upset and defended myself and told her what I thought about her. Anyway, in the end, I just walked out of class and that's when I woke up. Bloody hell! I actually took a test in art history today and I couldn't stop thinking about that dream. It freaks me out cause I wouldn't do that kinda stuff. Man, my grades suck.

<FONT color=#339999>Hey guys! It's finally Friday! Ugh, I'm tired. I like took a nap during my Spanish class =/ Well, yeah. I'll get to see my Chris today so yeah, that's gonna be cool. Haha, I cut my hair like on Tuesday night and like people just noticed it today. I think that it is because I have had my hair worn up until today. Haha, I cut it myself that's why it looks a little funny and stuff. I guess I did it because I was really fustrated with the way it looked and I needed a cut anyway.</FONT>
HEY! Haha, I'm still on to this =) Anyway. I'm pretty good today! I feel great! I'm listening to Finch. They so rock! Everyone should listen to Finch! YEAH!!!!!
